{"title":"艺术","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":512,"tags":["DFS"],"operation":{"submit":"https://syzoj.com/problem/722#submit_code","submissions":"https://syzoj.com/submissions?problem_id=722","statistics":"https://syzoj.com/problem/722/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://syzoj.com/problem/722/testdata","discussion":"https://syzoj.com/discussion/problem/722"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"小L是一名艺术家，这天他接受了一个“制作插花环\"的委托，制作一个由 $n$ 个花瓶组成的环。\r\n\r\n在小L看来，相邻两个花瓶如果高度相差超过k那它们就是不美的。\r\n\r\n小L会告诉你花瓶的数量以及每个花瓶的高度 $a_i$ ，请你帮助他计算符合\"美\"的要求的方案数。"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"第一行两个整数 $n,k$ 。\r\n接下来每行一个整数 $a_i$ 表示一个花瓶的高度"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"一个整数表示符合\"美\"的要求的方案数"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"**input**\r\n```\r\n4 10\r\n2\r\n16\r\n6\r\n10\r\n```\r\n**output**\r\n```\r\n2\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"$1≤n≤10$\r\n\r\n$1≤k,a_i≤1,000,000$"}]}